dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.phy.PhysicalResource
dataStructure.description:
This is an abstract base class for describing different types of hardware that constitute a Product. It has two main purposes: (1) to collect common attributes and relationships for all hardware, and (2) to provide a convenient, single point where relationships with other managed objects can be defined. The HasWarrantyInfo association (not shown) describes warranty information of hardware.

This entity is abstract

This entity is optional
